::Dark One::

"I'm afraid I can't let you out," says Dark One, still over his intercom, 
"You won't make it very far on your own anyhow."

He pauses for a while, leaving most of her questions unanswered as the window 
she had been looking out of darkened and finally went completely black. "Rest 
for now. We'll arrive shortly."
